t: "fala tdefu -ayha almuminun biallah wrswlh- ean jhad almshrkyn, wtjbunu ean qtalhm, wtdewhm 'iilaa alslh walmsalmt, wa'antum alqahrwn lahum walealwn elyhm, wallah taealaa maeakum binasrih wtayydh. wafi dhlk bisharat ezymt bialnasr walzzafar ealaa alaeda'. walan yunqskm allah thawab aemalkm"